- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and word embeddings. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new algorithm for learning neural embeddings. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper discusses document embeddings and their use in topic modeling. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a new algorithm for learning representations of words, topics, documents, authors, etc. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the performance of the proposed algorithm compared to state-of-the-art models.
